<h4 id="file-prep">File Prep</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Make sure files are organized
    <ul>
      <li>InDesign file</li>
      <li>Linked images folder</li>
      <li>Native images folder
        <ul>
          <li>raster files</li>
          <li>vector files</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>NO fonts folder - only Adobe Fonts</li>
      <li>Research folder
        <ul>
          <li>Photo research</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Text files
        <ul>
          <li>Original text files</li>
          <li>Cleaned up text files</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>All placed raster images single-layer .psd files</li>
  <li>All placed vector files single-layer .ai files</li>
  <li>Fonts (if any) in placed Illustrator or Photoshop files are outlined in a duplicate file</li>
  <li>The only fonts in the InDesign document are the ones in use
    <ul>
      <li>No default Minion Pro</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>No spot colours throughout the project</li>
  <li>Bleeds are exactly 1/8‚Äù, no bigger, no smaller</li>
</ul>

