<h4 id="pdf-for-print">PDF for Print</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Output to PDF using an appropriate PDF preset</li>
  <li>Bleeds, crop marks &amp; colour bars</li>
  <li>In Acrobat: File &gt; Document Properties &gt; Open Fit to Screen with Pages panel</li>
  <li>Imposed booklet</li>
  <li>1/8‚Äù bleeds - precisely.</li>
  <li>CMYK colour mode</li>
  <li>Crop marks</li>
</ul>

